{"tid":100060,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[重post] [看圖說故事]  獨遊西葡","createTime":"2017-01-29T16:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T18:29:50.000Z","uid":32932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbc3a737442220cdf29396d11d26cda8ac3856f","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"之前係舊登Post過 但未打完 搬過黎繼續打<br />\n另外係第2個post講緊保加利亞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/94619/page/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F94619%2Fpage%2F3&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxML%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e0b99001\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/94619/page/3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一路upload先覺得各位巴絲打遊記好詳細好勁 <br />\n淨係upload圖已經煩到想喊<br />\n仲有十幾個國家想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 今年<span style=\"color: red;\">(而家已經係上年啦)</span>四月果陣見Barcelona好似幾靚，<br />\n機票又好平，於是就狗衝左機票 <br />\n(全個旅程交通包括兩程火車、一程夜車、四程飛機 <br />\n2000hkd有找 實數唔記得啦 太耐之前)<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後Barcelona係我比較上最冇咁鍾意既地方 <br />\n不過今次旅程都係好開心 <br />\n除左中間有d甩轆同埋有D小意外之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發之前其實淆晒底 第一次真正自己毒遊 仲要自己訓通宵火車、通宵巴士、機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前半獨遊過新加坡 但西班牙治安出名唔好 搞到我都心驚驚<br />\n不過最後無俾人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西班牙治安比我想像中好 <br />\n不過我有強勁既防盜方法，有機會再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁成個旅程就去左葡萄牙3個城市：Porto, Lisbon, Sintra<br />\n同埋西班牙2個城市：Seville, Barcelona<br />\n<br />\n咁我果陣就係瑞典exchange緊，所以就由瑞典出發<br />\n由瑞典出發搭夜車去Copenhagen <br />\n10am抵達Copenhagen，係Copenhagen半日遊 <br />\n行左Copenhagen大半景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後7pm上機去Porto 原定大概10:30pm抵步 <br />\n但搭Ryanair delay左一個鐘頭搞到我連尾班地鐵都走埋 <br />\n之後上左迷你穿梭小巴 架車得我一個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n車費$5eur，落車既時候我得$10eur <br />\n但司機找唔到錢俾我 最後司機冇無收我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超感動<br />\n我愛葡萄牙大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b281cc3507ec787eb5d4cf3c8767a8d73172ff","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/5r6ns3slj/IMG_0672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2F5r6ns3slj%2FIMG_0672.jpg&h=2f2f5efa&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/kjiwx8x75/IMG_0713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fkjiwx8x75%2FIMG_0713.jpg&h=f36b07d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波爾圖的街道(左)   世上最美的書店(右)：Harry Potter中會移動的樓梯的靈感在此產生<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/p1hmpo31r/IMG_1075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fp1hmpo31r%2FIMG_1075.jpg&h=52310bc9&s={SIZE}\" />   <img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/6zdq8xiy7/IMG_1326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2F6zdq8xiy7%2FIMG_1326.jpg&h=ba2da59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波爾圖的街道(左)    波爾圖的河岸(右) <br />\n<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/4uiuhod0j/IMG_1529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2F4uiuhod0j%2FIMG_1529.jpg&h=359bbbb6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/iv385dtad/IMG_1532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2Fiv385dtad%2FIMG_1532.jpg&h=59f235c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波爾圖的夜景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/3xqe06481/IMG_1590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F3xqe06481%2FIMG_1590.jpg&h=5aec8858&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/jrvon179t/IMG_1668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fjrvon179t%2FIMG_1668.jpg&h=55c39380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波爾圖的街道(左)   葡萄牙電車內觀(右)"},{"pid":"77f3a9b5c566d4698da48334966843fcfc8f8c16","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"正皮加速"},{"pid":"3a3561e1dc6f40e53c6d34b28be5f4fee3644576","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"係Porto三晚，住係一間叫Tattva Design Hostel Porto既hostel<br />\n呢個hostel幾高質，間房有自己廁所 有兩三格沖涼房同埋廁所 同埋幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包早餐，床有簾 夠私隱 唔怕柒到喊既睡相俾人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙葡萄牙係幾多hostel既地方，好多百幾蚊晚 平得黎又靚既hostel<br />\n所以如果去西班牙葡萄牙旅行都推薦大家住下hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聖本篤火車站Estacao de Sao Bento 係我第一個去到既景點<br />\n因為第一晚一落車就係呢個火車站<br />\n而我間hostel都係呢個火車站附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1429129122-2332850857_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1429129122-2332850857_l.jpg&h=a4dda913&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1429129122-4058148350_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1429129122-4058148350_l.jpg&h=a230e845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n偷左人地兩張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為我d相返到香港之後唔見左一大部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n火車站入面有充滿葡式風情既藍色瓷磚畫 畫入面係講葡萄牙既歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我去到果陣已經凌晨 兩個職員眼望望咁 毒撚我偷影左兩張相即刻急急腳走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cc67abc08174f2cf0736b9b35c33214f3a1bb5","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"第二日一起身係Hostel食左個自助早餐，質素唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過Porto好多好野食，記住唔好塞飽自己，要留肚食葡國菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 牧師塔<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/6a3048e88d330af35d168d5b14704963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F6a3048e88d330af35d168d5b14704963.jpg&h=196a8fd0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/ppp59uzeh/IMG_0915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fppp59uzeh%2FIMG_0915.jpg&h=9bc7f00f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牧師塔(左) 塔上風光(右)<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/rvjg4d2ux/IMG_0913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Frvjg4d2ux%2FIMG_0913.jpg&h=8c6c11f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/v64ge0w5h/IMG_0933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2Fv64ge0w5h%2FIMG_0933.jpg&h=96fefb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔上風光(左&amp;右)<br />\n<img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/3nvi9li9x/IMG_0921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2F3nvi9li9x%2FIMG_0921.jpg&h=8c7e0ff4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/5470rql6t/IMG_0922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2F5470rql6t%2FIMG_0922.jpg&h=c9b7e345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔上風光(左&amp;右)<br />\n<br />\n巴洛克式教士教堂，牧場塔高 76 米，有六層，係1763年建成<br />\n曾經係當時整個葡萄牙最高既建築物<br />\n要參觀係需要買門票，買完門票之後就可以行上去啦<br />\n沿途上去係有d展覽咁樣俾人邊行邊停低休息下，佢個idea都幾聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理性少少講句，雖然都係靚既，但Porto老城區唔係我見過最靚既歐洲老城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.Livraria Lello 萊羅書店<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/q85ime4n5/IMG_0711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fq85ime4n5%2FIMG_0711.jpg&h=d7e4c02b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/fjh0a9bbn/IMG_0717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Ffjh0a9bbn%2FIMG_0717.jpg&h=bd6a3d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n書店內實拍(左&amp;右)：長期人山人海<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1443262007-200265990_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1443262007-200265990_l.jpg&h=2e4aadca&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1443262004-2750628327_l.jpg?v=1443262007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1443262004-2750628327_l.jpg%3Fv%3D1443262007&h=8c864e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(對唔住我影d相真係好樣衰 忍唔住上網搵人地影既相share出黎俾大家睇 <br />\n我驚大家見到我影既垃圾相唔想去)</span></span><br />\n創辦於1906年，是葡萄牙最具歷史的書店之一，曾被孤獨星球選為第三大最美書店。<br />\n作為一個偽文青，梗係要入去扮下睇書拍下風格圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人話JK羅林後生&amp;#22000;陣住過Porto一段時間<br />\n呢間書店係佢成日流連既地方，而呢間書店正中央一條好特別既樓梯帶左靈感俾佢<br />\n呢條樓梯就係Harry Potter入面個條移動樓梯既原型啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦，相信我去完書店打卡一定都會寫出驚天地泣鬼神既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為太多人想去參觀書店，書店而家要買門票先可以參觀 同埋有人潮管制措施<br />\n係對面馬路一間紅色亭到買飛 同職員講想參與書店 之後俾$3EUR 就可以入去書店瘋狂打卡<br />\n呢$3EUR可以抵銷返係書店買書既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過只可以買書，紀念品、文具係唔抵銷得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我買左本葡萄牙填色畫冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當紀念品一流，雖然到而家都未開封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92964d7ff79c33ed35ea53390c1dd88eb9d5bb12","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"3. Igreja do Carmo &amp; lgreja dos Camrmelitas 藍磚教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/wavrb0c3j/IMG_0867.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fwavrb0c3j%2FIMG_0867.jpg&h=77e31933&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/qt7h3qqgp/IMG_0872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fqt7h3qqgp%2FIMG_0872.jpg&h=f2ee1935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍磚教堂外觀(左&amp;右)<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1443285356-3428109974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1443285356-3428109974.jpg&h=4855a09b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/travelmous2013/1443284057-987882660_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftravelmous2013%2F1443284057-987882660_l.jpg&h=fa26b787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(對唔住又忍唔住偷左人圖 我說服唔到自己下面講到好似好靚咁 但上面D圖咁柒) </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲教堂好多，半年內參觀嘅教堂我諗大概有五十個<br />\n半年內一直睇教堂教堂教堂，已經審美疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但葡萄牙嘅教堂風格令我印象好深<br />\n葡萄牙的教堂同其他建築真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以每次在轉角見到小小的藍磚教堂驚喜都忍唔住飛過去影相<br />\n<br />\n以上教堂內跟一般的教堂大同小異，所以就唔放圖了 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(利申：懶屎忽)</span><br />\n<br />\n順便post後兩天見到的藍磚教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/emf1gk5qb/IMG_1594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Femf1gk5qb%2FIMG_1594.jpg&h=1f6c8efd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/8so9ap1af/IMG_1605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2F8so9ap1af%2FIMG_1605.jpg&h=80711be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChurch of Saint Ildefonso 外觀(左&amp;右)：興建於18世紀 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/ml2o6bs1z/IMG_1604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fml2o6bs1z%2FIMG_1604.jpg&h=30fe9e9b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/v8kgy2v9j/IMG_1609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fv8kgy2v9j%2FIMG_1609.jpg&h=afcaf1be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChurch of Saint Ildefonso 內部 (左)       Capela Das Almas(右)：藏身在小巷轉角的小藍磚教堂<br />\n<br />\n[size=2]第一日既朝早 編排既行程已經行左七七八八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔緊要 因為葡萄牙最靚既地方唔係D景點<br />\n而係街頭巷尾既小房子 又或者路上突然見到瓷磚 會忍唔住一直影一直影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚係瑣細既小細節上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  葡萄牙係我去左咁多國家之中其中一個最鍾意既國家<br />\n講唔出邊個景點特別吸引我 因為佢靚既唔係D咩特別宏偉既建築或者教堂<br />\n而家成條街都好靚好靚好靚 成個城市都好靚好靚好靚 成個國家都好靚好靚好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c28eecb22d477a490b0324821a854c76e7f744d","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"睇完書店、牧師塔同教堂之後 就去左食野 <br />\n係條街上面fing左好耐 見到間餐廳有Francesinha三文治<br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/4h5ctv7jb/IMG_0864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2F4h5ctv7jb%2FIMG_0864.jpg&h=8e926072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrancesinha三文治係Porto獨有既食物<br />\n之前睇左旅遊節目，見到主持都有介紹 所以就走左去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/kobn9xejr/IMG_0861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fkobn9xejr%2FIMG_0861.jpg&h=0ea79c90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/nkyoa7kdj/IMG_0863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fnkyoa7kdj%2FIMG_0863.jpg&h=b4351370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個三文治+薯條 ~$4,5EUR<br />\n<br />\n入面係火腿、肉片、葡國腸，<br />\n上面有芝士同埋半熟雞蛋，<br />\n最後再淋特製醬汁上去<br />\n<br />\n一開始食落口都幾好食，食食下覺得有D咸<br />\n如果有朋友兩個share應該會ok d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我估可能係d火腿出事 西班牙火腿又係幾咸下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋葡萄牙既薯條都係圖入面咁樣<br />\n好似放到淋晒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得葡萄牙人口味同我地平時口味有d似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n葡萄牙野食食親都有種好似好熟悉既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nso far 都幾好食 好過西班牙嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4305d7172e953bd2961e19177601c343ae2cf571","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"食完野9fing左一陣就諗住去河邊坐下，再去另一面新城區探下險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/5pqumfa2p/IMG_1084_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F5pqumfa2p%2FIMG_1084_2.jpg&h=bfcc5da1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/4bz7r4atd/IMG_1085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F4bz7r4atd%2FIMG_1085.jpg&h=c00089f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完大斜路落斜之後就去到河岸邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/89mhgixmp/IMG_1086.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F89mhgixmp%2FIMG_1086.jpg&h=5825eca7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/m4kryzs1t/IMG_1087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fm4kryzs1t%2FIMG_1087.jpg&h=46ef8b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岸邊既建築(左&amp;右)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行到落去就見到 路易一世大橋 Ponte de Dom Luis I <br />\n呢條橋係Porto最出名既地標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/v2ox9z8sz/IMG_1182.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Fv2ox9z8sz%2FIMG_1182.jpg&h=c5f10a5b&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/xy20gucsz/IMG_1183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Fxy20gucsz%2FIMG_1183.jpg&h=ea8f67af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條橋係由大名鼎鼎既 巴黎鐵塔設計師&mdash;居斯塔夫&middot;艾菲爾Alexandre Gustave Eiffe<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個徒弟設計架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (呢件事其實有咩好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s16.postimg.org/rtewv3gpx/IMG_1178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs16.postimg.org%2Frtewv3gpx%2FIMG_1178.jpg&h=b37004b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀光船 窮撚我坐唔起 影左當坐左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n另外留意下橋既右手邊白色圓圓地果舊就係我之後既目的地 <br />\n係欣賞Porto舊城同河岸既好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/ft3ewu6pl/IMG_1189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fft3ewu6pl%2FIMG_1189.jpg&h=cb70f70d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/69tq3dj7d/IMG_1190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F69tq3dj7d%2FIMG_1190.jpg&h=da200aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就經條天橋行去新城啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到新城區之後望返去舊城區 嘩！靚到傻左！！！！！！<br />\n認真用類似背景影左超過兩百張自拍+風格圖+風景圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/ummov4gyr/IMG_1295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Fummov4gyr%2FIMG_1295.jpg&h=e03bd1ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/xw141l52b/IMG_1302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Fxw141l52b%2FIMG_1302.jpg&h=e736019e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/70r2moo2r/IMG_1304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2F70r2moo2r%2FIMG_1304.jpg&h=7d9c0181&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/4r7jpo4ir/IMG_1326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2F4r7jpo4ir%2FIMG_1326.jpg&h=e12b3cc5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airpano.com/files/360video/Video-Porto/images/image1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airpano.com%2Ffiles%2F360video%2FVideo-Porto%2Fimages%2Fimage1.jpg&h=7d5f4000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好啦其實我影得好樣衰 所以我已經準備左其他人影既相俾大家睇</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7db958d1814e3ce7e87f0212ef44399da7c2fba","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"介紹返先 加亞新城 (簡稱新城) 係葡萄牙產酒區<br />\n城入面有好多酒廠酒窖 好多人都會參觀同埋試酒<br />\n不過因為我唔識飲同埋唔太鍾意飲既關係 就冇安排呢個行程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，繼續講！<br />\n<br />\n影夠風格圖之後，就開始闖上去之前講白色圓圓地既建築啦<br />\n本身打算係上個個位睇日落，不過我就冇跟地圖，純粹自己亂咁行。<br />\n走入橫街窄巷冒下險。<br />\n<br />\n沿途影既：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/efgpt5fqp/IMG_1332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fefgpt5fqp%2FIMG_1332.jpg&h=e0a4eec0&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n真．葡國雞(左)：呢隻雞係葡萄牙代表物之一<br />\n傳說佢顯靈拯救左一個無辜既朝聖者，所以佢有公正、信任和好運既象徵，係葡萄牙既吉詳物<br />\n呢張相入面個隻係全世界最大既葡萄牙公雞公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/wjjqdsdf5/IMG_1335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fwjjqdsdf5%2FIMG_1335.jpg&h=fd4bde70&s={SIZE}\" />   <img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/iedxbz4dt/IMG_1338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fiedxbz4dt%2FIMG_1338.jpg&h=567b91af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新城比舊城冷清好多(左)  沿路有D廢棄建築、有D流浪貓(右)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再順住D山既小巷、廢棄建築行左十分鐘左右 果陣沿路已經一個人都冇<br />\n之後好開心咁行呀行<br />\n我 撞 到  一男一女啪啪啪緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地冇著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我望住佢地 佢地又望住我 <br />\n我即刻華麗轉身跑走扮無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個下真心淆底驚佢過黎滅我口<br />\n諗諗下都幾危險 好彩今次係阻人扑野&amp;#21867; <br />\n下次撞到人劈友或者咩罪行 我客死異鄉都唔知發生咩事 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/v8gkj2775/IMG_1342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fv8gkj2775%2FIMG_1342.jpg&h=16aa927b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亂行搵到個幾靚既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/aqvm7ev3l/IMG_1344.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Faqvm7ev3l%2FIMG_1344.jpg&h=42cb6ac2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/h3arh8y5t/IMG_1343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fh3arh8y5t%2FIMG_1343.jpg&h=10123b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新城區既小巷"},{"pid":"8aa7ff4f42a5ee8d6422f2cd1b33bedbe82697dc","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"撞破完人地啪啪啪之後，我就滾水淥腳咁走返舊城啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/pmgj8qemx/IMG_1374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fpmgj8qemx%2FIMG_1374.jpg&h=fe9ce3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係舊城果面見到貓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/tk3sy51g9/IMG_1375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Ftk3sy51g9%2FIMG_1375.jpg&h=15a7f93c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/uoxv3inx5/IMG_1377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fuoxv3inx5%2FIMG_1377.jpg&h=c0dec614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由廣場附近   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/hw9r3lcbd/IMG_1376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fhw9r3lcbd%2FIMG_1376.jpg&h=a41665bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一間非常靚既美式大型連鎖餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：McDonald<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真 Porto景點之一 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/yml4sxaqh/IMG_1378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fyml4sxaqh%2FIMG_1378.jpg&h=60360049&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/eghmu1f2x/IMG_1380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Feghmu1f2x%2FIMG_1380.jpg&h=136ea77b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行去食飯沿途<br />\n<br />\n之後入左一間睇旅遊節目介紹既烤雞店：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/xzm83eduh/IMG_1381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fxzm83eduh%2FIMG_1381.jpg&h=a2fde9e6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/4yhvtzteh/IMG_1382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F4yhvtzteh%2FIMG_1382.jpg&h=be9a6627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd烤雞味係條街到已經聞到 真心好鬼香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯呢餐飯應該$5-7EUR左右     半隻雞+薯條+可樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/m0fb9txnd/IMG_1383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fm0fb9txnd%2FIMG_1383.jpg&h=b895113b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n間店唔係做遊客生意 間店得圖入面呢個靚仔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/4oeyoe461/IMG_1384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F4oeyoe461%2FIMG_1384.jpg&h=61ff75f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間店好多大叔，好地道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢地邊食邊睇波 好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間餐廳真係一個本地女人都冇 好麻甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 葡萄牙西班牙餐廳都好興呢類BAR&amp;#26545; 之後張&amp;#27336;勁高fuck 玩我麼?<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 葡萄牙餐廳食飯D麵包係要收費架 記得唔好亂食人地D麵包<br />\n你唔要既話 好似就咁放係到就得 <br />\n食完飯俾錢果陣，佢見你冇掂過D麵包就唔會收你錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩晚餐旁邊有間食豬扒包非常非常出名既店，叫Conga<br />\n不過我好飽食唔落包，所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  叫左甜品<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/wd1lvwr6h/IMG_1388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fwd1lvwr6h%2FIMG_1388.jpg&h=f4a88128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有第2個胃食甜品 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完都唔知乜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n外面炸既 入面係雪糕 仲有cream 好邪惡嗚呀<br />\n勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e289b081fd32f3a0a4ebd2b32aa627f0e991ec","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"食完飯+甜品之後個天已經黑晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/v5foz8rf5/IMG_1393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fv5foz8rf5%2FIMG_1393.jpg&h=94470d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由廣場again<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/8urtz9u4x/IMG_1402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2F8urtz9u4x%2FIMG_1402.jpg&h=150ae969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知咩building 見幾靚就影左<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/roi8a0hqp/IMG_1403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Froi8a0hqp%2FIMG_1403.jpg&h=8385a359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔記得左做咩影人間店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似俾間店d公仔嚇親<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/3ysslbjdd/IMG_1404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2F3ysslbjdd%2FIMG_1404.jpg&h=930d448e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始講個個火車站既外觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚睇幾靚<br />\n<br />\n想睇鐵橋夜景 又落返河邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/ikjt9kg5t/IMG_1408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fikjt9kg5t%2FIMG_1408.jpg&h=53585c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條鐵橋夜晚睇靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/yk2gt4c7l/IMG_1409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fyk2gt4c7l%2FIMG_1409.jpg&h=bb0748fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0bec575feed9e481f8220031074cb06b81790b7","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"之後我又打算挑戰中午挑戰失敗個個圓形打卡位<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/42l8fja0b/IMG_1521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2F42l8fja0b%2FIMG_1521.jpg&h=939be2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又過左橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/5iwqxocx7/IMG_1523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2F5iwqxocx7%2FIMG_1523.jpg&h=60eafe09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次跟住google map行。真心行到粗口都講埋 <br />\n睇相同地圖好似好近咁 但佢係咁兜路 條路仲鬼死咁斜 45度都有fuck fuck <br />\n本身呢區中午已經冷清 入黑之後成個area一個人都冇 自己一個人行勁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/45542ddnv/IMG_1524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2F45542ddnv%2FIMG_1524.jpg&h=f327454a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左好耐終於睇到夜景同埋見到目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 孝感動天呀你老味<br />\n不過仲要再兜大路先去到最高個位，即係圓形建築物既門口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/tcg02mgrv/IMG_1529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Ftcg02mgrv%2FIMG_1529.jpg&h=e6ba8d60&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/hd4hvbb6z/IMG_1532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fhd4hvbb6z%2FIMG_1532.jpg&h=3a85de01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/5pf1eibfv/IMG_1534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2F5pf1eibfv%2FIMG_1534.jpg&h=5cc2ebbc&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/5166vkcq3/IMG_1541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2F5166vkcq3%2FIMG_1541.jpg&h=fd680f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個位見到既夜景已經幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/hh2wpb623/IMG_1542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fhh2wpb623%2FIMG_1542.jpg&h=0b0fd87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於上到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  行左超過半個鐘大斜路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/cm97r17qj/IMG_1555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fcm97r17qj%2FIMG_1555.jpg&h=697d50eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高炒條橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/cc1p7ot4b/IMG_1557_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fcc1p7ot4b%2FIMG_1557_2.jpg&h=c6b0bf06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後返hostel沖涼訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/ovxaesy97/IMG_1586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fovxaesy97%2FIMG_1586.jpg&h=4ab77a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/n5e9dbgq3/IMG_1587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fn5e9dbgq3%2FIMG_1587.jpg&h=5edabf59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76dfe08170148ecedcd8d159ac9e6a33c4323b10","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"第2日起身又係hostel食自助早餐<br />\n無記錯既話好似係有自助pancake機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係特別鍾意食pancake，不過自己整係幾好玩既<br />\n<br />\n之後去左行之前講過既教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再之後就去左波爾圖傳統市場 Mercado do Bolhao<br />\n平時去旅行都好鍾意去傳統市場同埋Supermarket睇下有咩特別既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/i39invq89/IMG_1611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fi39invq89%2FIMG_1611.jpg&h=e18eba4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/s1uhacznt/IMG_1612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fs1uhacznt%2FIMG_1612.jpg&h=b8434542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市場有一半已經冇營業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n市場有花檔、糕點檔、生果檔、醃製肉檔 同埋有賣紀念品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/rswwkfmvd/IMG_1617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Frswwkfmvd%2FIMG_1617.jpg&h=af576f46&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/ojihdyyrt/IMG_1613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fojihdyyrt%2FIMG_1613.jpg&h=8287e09c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/3nw72q2kp/IMG_1615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F3nw72q2kp%2FIMG_1615.jpg&h=dcf44c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/55hnea7bd/IMG_1618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F55hnea7bd%2FIMG_1618.jpg&h=d1da0a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次係葡萄牙食既葡萄牙 <br />\n中間好creamy 似吉士撻 <br />\n雖然都好食既 但味道同口感同我想像中有d出入<br />\n不過遲d去Lisbon葡撻始創店食既葡撻盲就似我地平時食開既葡撻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/mwt9sqmq1/IMG_1619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fmwt9sqmq1%2FIMG_1619.jpg&h=2e8dc16d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/x85mleefd/IMG_1621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fx85mleefd%2FIMG_1621.jpg&h=77e365da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市場入面都有幾間餐廳 我就係是旦揀左一間 係入面食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/qvqhbkbd5/IMG_1623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fqvqhbkbd5%2FIMG_1623.jpg&h=fed92af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同來自London既一家三口同&amp;#26545; 圖入面係仔仔<br />\n之後爸爸見我手機個廣角鏡好得意就撩我傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爸爸同我講完野之後 仔仔就開始係咁同我講野<br />\n仔仔係素食者黎，但爸爸媽媽食肉<br />\n於是爸爸媽媽是旦叫左薯條俾佢食就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自首，其實同佢傾左一陣計都唔知其實佢係男定女<br />\n佢勁Cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   勁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁問我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我知佢地一家係London係開英文學校(?) 會接待想學英文既外國留學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/irid6toy1/IMG_1624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Firid6toy1%2FIMG_1624.jpg&h=a5a1dda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔知叫乜好 見到menu張圖是旦點左呢個野<br />\n炸魚球飯    魚球入面好似有D菜有D薯仔?唔肯定咩黎但幾好食<br />\n葡萄牙既飯好神奇 佢煮果陣有落調味 就咁食都唔會覺得難以下嚥<br />\n不過葡萄牙食既米同我地食既泰國米唔同 都係泰國米好食D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35fe77273692184c0213cc77fe65b00256d5f90","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"上面漏左講<br />\n直到爸爸媽媽用'he'黎代稱個細路 我先firm到個細路係男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b515c7aee3f737cdbe0d28b5839c61ee47643672","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"市場：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/87413h3cp/IMG_1631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F87413h3cp%2FIMG_1631.jpg&h=23fc0201&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/vmly8tn3t/IMG_1632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fvmly8tn3t%2FIMG_1632.jpg&h=97589c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/kct8dvi2h/IMG_1634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fkct8dvi2h%2FIMG_1634.jpg&h=a065ffad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/m5w527395/IMG_1635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fm5w527395%2FIMG_1635.jpg&h=f5378d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/45mxxtb21/IMG_1639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2F45mxxtb21%2FIMG_1639.jpg&h=b40a6880&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/h4or0tvsp/IMG_1633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fh4or0tvsp%2FIMG_1633.jpg&h=4ee05284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市場二樓幾靚既店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/cqg9ozl89/IMG_1642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fcqg9ozl89%2FIMG_1642.jpg&h=84eba956&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/oi8qdj589/IMG_1644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Foi8qdj589%2FIMG_1644.jpg&h=07c21162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出左去之後見到d餐廳好似香港舊式鋪頭咁<br />\n覺得好吸引忍唔住買左一個黎食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fuck 唔好食既 嬲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/eaq714j09/IMG_1646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Feaq714j09%2FIMG_1646.jpg&h=f95c2142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路過一間葡撻店 佢講到自己好出名咁<br />\n加上之前食市場買果個葡撻同我想像中有d出入<br />\n所以我就又買左一個睇下係咪之前間店既問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係同之前市場買既差唔多 好似好食少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n街景：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/o6ra0ros9/IMG_1645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fo6ra0ros9%2FIMG_1645.jpg&h=843cb56a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/c7frtgj7d/IMG_1647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fc7frtgj7d%2FIMG_1647.jpg&h=fb798995&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6152f83524307e87b83d62fd32ef969fa1737f47","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙瓷磚：<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙瓷磚藝術係葡萄牙每一處都見到佢既蹤影。街頭、屋企裝飾、碗碟等等都唔難見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/m29w4r8m9/IMG_2568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fm29w4r8m9%2FIMG_2568.jpg&h=8d9c78c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/qmj94zyjh/IMG_1911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Fqmj94zyjh%2FIMG_1911.jpg&h=32dc3629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/qnt6yf0d9/IMG_1912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Fqnt6yf0d9%2FIMG_1912.jpg&h=fcc13668&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/bam0o7e93/IMG_1071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2Fbam0o7e93%2FIMG_1071.jpg&h=5a29617f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓷磚係摩爾人(即埃及人)引入歐洲既。但葡萄牙係直至15世紀先開始興起。<br />\n<br />\n當時葡國國王好欣賞西班牙格拉那達 阿爾罕布拉宮，所以係Sintra興趣宮殿時都要求加入大量瓷磚<br />\n<br />\n初時只係得淨色或者簡單圖案既瓷磚。<br />\n<br />\n後來係16世紀受西洋畫影響，令葡萄牙既瓷磚變得色彩繽紛。<br />\n<br />\n後來受明朝青花瓷影響，大量瓷磚以藍白為主色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/p8z8yrhuv/IMG_1365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fp8z8yrhuv%2FIMG_1365.jpg&h=02fbf5d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/fhg3oq6sz/IMG_0852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Ffhg3oq6sz%2FIMG_0852.jpg&h=ef8a9f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/lozco6m3x/IMG_1345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Flozco6m3x%2FIMG_1345.jpg&h=6b9b9d49&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/4i2rcezxp/IMG_1352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2F4i2rcezxp%2FIMG_1352.jpg&h=072f3e11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/yl9f52jn7/IMG_0849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fyl9f52jn7%2FIMG_0849.jpg&h=7f3b5959&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/vdcsrbgx9/IMG_1349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Fvdcsrbgx9%2FIMG_1349.jpg&h=f95b20f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s12.postimg.org/8pxjl61d9/IMG_1350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2F8pxjl61d9%2FIMG_1350.jpg&h=997959d2&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/a7b4xfmk3/IMG_0853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fa7b4xfmk3%2FIMG_0853.jpg&h=7b1a5edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPorto街頭瓷磚鳩拍"},{"pid":"fc07caf07fb1ded621f03d2daadeb60f091ccc11","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"唔記得左開始之前講<br />\n而家補返：<br />\n<br />\n第一日(6/4)：夜晚11pm去到Porto，直闖Hostel沖涼訓覺 <br />\n第四日(9/4)：中午搭飛機去Lisbon <br />\n第五日(10/4) Sintra一日遊，再加去左羅卡角打卡 <br />\n第六日(11/4) 8pm 搭夜車去西班牙Seville，第七日(12/4) 5am 抵達Seville <br />\n第九日(14/4) 8am 搭飛機去Barcelona <br />\n第十日(15/4) 8pm 搭飛機返Sweden <br />\n<br />\n扣除搭車時間，真正停留時間： <br />\nPorto 2日半 Lisbon 2日 Seville 2日 Barcelona 1日半"},{"pid":"cad8937870d8a9a9a2602900f77c186475b21116","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"之前打嘅去到呢到<br />\n<br />\n打完個保加利亞遊記再繼續<br />\n<br />\n有咩問我都會答大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389b1064a638f756c0fd3cdaef345aa96bded580","tid":100060,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"過癮"},{"pid":"f6666960b2b98bc018c38216f38e975db358445d","tid":100060,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"波圖除咗嗰舊炸包之外，佢啲牛雜都好出名<br />\n嗰陣差啲有衝動買罐罐頭牛雜返香港<br />\n不過最後都係放棄咗"},{"pid":"f920ab206531cf010e6c6a419ead7a260a6a484c","tid":100060,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波圖除咗嗰舊炸包之外，佢啲牛雜